querysource.name: test
querysource.sql: SELECT r.id_recibo AS numero, CONCAT( CONCAT( LPAD( r.serie, 5, 0 ), '-' ), LPAD( r.numero, 5, 0 ) ) AS NumSerie, DATE_FORMAT( r.fecha_pago, '%d %m %y' ) AS fecha, r.texto AS contenido, r.precio AS total, CONCAT( CONCAT( c.calle, CONCAT( ' ', c.numero ) ) ) AS direccion, c.razon_social AS cliente, c.`CUIT/CUIL` AS cuit FROM recibos AS r, clientes AS c WHERE r.id_recibo = <? value("id_recibo") ?> AND c.id = r.id_cliente;

querysource.name: recargos
querysource.sql: <? if( servicio ) ?> SELECT FROM recargos AS r, servicios AS s WHERE id_servicio = <? value( "id_servicio" ); ?> <? endif ?>
